OL,7,FA father has described the
OL,8,F"petrifying" moment a rollercoaster
OL,9,Fhis son was on derailed a the Coney
OL,10,FBeach Pleasure Park on Wednesday
OL,11,Fevening.
OL,13,F13 children and an adult were treated
OL,14,Ffor minor injuries after the ride
OL,15,Fderailed at the well-known Porthcawl
OL,16,Famusement park. Others at the park
OL,17,Fsaid they heard "horrific screams"
OL,18,Fwhen it happened.
