OL,7,FPolice said 14 people suffered
OL,8,Finjuries in the incident, with seven
OL,9,Ftaken to hospital for treatment.
OL,11,FThe operators of the park said the
OL,12,Fincident involved a "third-party ride
OL,13,Fnot owned by Coney Beach".
OL,15,FOne of the children on the ride was
OL,16,FIsaac. His Dad, Sam Conibear, said he
OL,17,Fand the family had visited the theme
OL,18,Fpark with some friends.
