OL,7,FHe said: "It was supposed to be a nice
OL,8,Fday, and we got there, it was a lovely
OL,9,Fday, even though the sun went out. We
OL,10,Fplanned to have a nice evening on the
OL,11,Fride."
OL,13,FAccording to eyewitnesses, just after
OL,14,F6pm part of the fairground's Wacky
OL,15,FWorm ride came off the tracks.
OL,17,F"It was loads of screaming - the kids
OL,18,Fwere petrified", Sam said.
