OL,7,F"I ran over there as fast as I could,"
OL,8,Fhe said.
OL,10,F"I jumped on the rollercoaster and got
OL,11,Fmy son off. Something just came over
OL,12,Fme - I just got on there and brought
OL,13,Finjured kids down to other dads."
OL,15,FSam Coniber said: "I looked up and I
OL,16,Fsaw Isaac screaming to get him off,
OL,17,Fand then my mate John flew onto the
OL,18,Fride and he got everyone on it.
