OL,7,F"(He) had his nose pouring with blood;
OL,8,Fit was shocking. I was absolutely
OL,9,Fpetrified, I was shaking in fear for
OL,10,Fhim, and then I saw this track
OL,11,Fderailing. I thought he was gonna end
OL,12,Fup on the floor."
OL,14,FIssac said: "I hit my face on the
OL,15,Frailing, and then, because of how hard
OL,16,Fit stopped. One of the railings bent
OL,17,Fup so it was like a really hard crash,
OL,18,Fand I hit my face on the bar."
