OL,7,FSouth Wales Police confirmed 13
OL,8,Fchildren had been injured in the
OL,9,Fincident. Seven people were taken to
OL,10,Fthe hospital by ambulance.
OL,12,FSam Coniber took his son to the
OL,13,Fhospital on Thursday morning. He said
OL,14,Fhe was told Issac may have broken his
OL,15,Fnose in the crash.
OL,17,FEyewitnesses who had children on the
OL,18,Fride said the incident has also taken
OL,19,Fan emotional toll. "(I'm) still shaken
OL,20,Fup. Yeah, I'm barely on no sleep, just
OL,21,Fkeeping an eye on Isaac," said Sam.
