OL,7,FJohn-Paul added: "It was horrible what
OL,8,Fhappened to the little kids, but it
OL,9,Fcould've been a lot worse."
OL,11,FThe Health and Safety Executive said
OL,12,Finvestigators have visited the site.
OL,13,FIn a statement, it said: "We are aware
OL,14,Fof this incident and are being
OL,15,Fsupported by South Wales Police. Our
OL,16,Finspectors are attending the site
OL,17,Ftoday to commence enquiries."
