OL,7,FIn a statement, the operator of the
OL,8,Fpark said: "Due to an incident on a
OL,9,Fthird-party ride not owned by Coney
OL,10,FBeach, we were instructed by the
OL,11,Fpolice to clear the site for further
OL,12,Finvestigation.
OL,14,F"We apologise for the disruption and
OL,15,Fwill be providing refunds to affected
OL,16,Fguests as soon as possible. We will be
OL,17,Freleasing instructions on refunds
OL,18,Fshortly."
